info.author: Ilkka Tuohela
info.description:
This module contains classes to read MacDive 2.0 sqlite database. 

Purpose is not to modify the database, the program itself is better for this,
but the scripts in this package allow you to export to additional formats and
quickly review the database contents.
info.name: macdive
info.html_description:
This module contains classes to read MacDive 2.0 sqlite database.

Purpose is not to modify the database, the program itself is better for this, but the scripts in this package allow you to export to additional formats and quickly review the database contents.
